We recommended that the Municipal Mayor through the GAD Focal Person:

facilitate the preparation of the GAD Agenda as well as the updating and completion of the needed data for a functional GAD database pursuant to PCW-DILG-DBM-NEDA JMC No. 2013-01, as amended by PCW-DILG-DBM-NEDA JMC No. 2016-01 as basis in the preparation of the annual GPB and GAD AR; 

